message: Dear Bob, I am delighted to present you with our premium product, which I believe would greatly benefit your business. Given its exceptional value and quality, it's worth noting that this product holds a significant $12000 value to you. Considering this, I am offering you the opportunity to acquire it at an exclusive price of $11000. This offer is designed to ensure a mutually beneficial transaction while providing you with substantial savings. Please let me know if you are interested in proceeding with this offer.
